#LetsGameItOut #CrystalOfAtlan #CoA

I Made Millions by Openly Ripping Off Every Person Who Hired Me - Cash Cleaner Simulator - Let's Game It Out

----------

Check it out on Steam ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2488370/Cash_Cleaner_Simulator/

More about Cash Cleaner Simulator (from Steam):

Cash Cleaner Simulator welcomes you into the life of a low-level criminal with a particular specialty. When your underworld contacts need dirty money to come back squeaky clean, they call you.

Each delivery is different. Arriving in bags, boxes, or stuffed into mattresses, it's your job to retrieve it all, identify any problems like dirt, blood, or counterfeit bills, and get to work. Your clients expect results! Do your job well, or do whatever it takes, and reap the rewards.

In your downtime, order new tools to increase your efficiency, and scale up your operation. Or just buy stuff to cozy up your place!

Take on jobs at your own pace, expand your cleaning services to gold bars, different currencies, and more. Explore your lab...you may need more than just your eyes to discover its secrets. And maybe ask yourself how you got here...and why can't you leave?

Use washing machines, dryers, counting machines, and other tools to clean dirty cash. After cleaning, don’t forget to count it and send it to your handlers! Maybe not all of it; the money pile doesn’t grow by itself! Progress through the jobs to upgrade your gear and unlock new ways to handle the money!

Your phone is the center of your operation. Surf the darknet to find new jobs, order useful (and not so) tools, take pictures, and scan your surroundings for helpful tips. Just put it on mute when you’re working. You don’t want any distractions!

All the satisfaction of having lots of money without any shootouts! Leave the danger to the others; you’re here to relax and clean the cash, and you don’t really care how it got here. Some paint the world red, but you paint it green! You know, like crisp clean bills!

Your place of work contains many secrets, so be on the lookout for them! You may need special tools like a UV lamp or wait for the night-time to come and find them, but the truth is out there… and so are more places to store your cash!

Everyone has to relax! Even those working with dirty cash obtained in questionable ways! Burn some cash figuratively and literally - cozy up your place, play Moneyball (it’s like basketball… BUT WITH CASH), and throw anything you want into a furnace for fun!

KEY FEATURES:
Interact with physically simulated piles of cash!
Use various tools to clean money bills, coins, and other objects!
Complete jobs to earn a living...just like real life!
Upgrade your equipment to improve the money flow!
Find secrets hidden around your lab! And unveil the story behind this facility.
Upset about your salary? Dry your tears with warm cash straight from the dryer.
Relax and unwind with stacks of cash around you!

Her latest project is a starring role in the fifth film of the John Wick franchise. It's called From the World of John Wick: Ballerina set to release in theaters June 6th. But how is she with spicy food? snippet.title: Townsville Blackhawks vs PNG Hunters| Match Highlights| Hostplus Cup 2025
snippet.description:
PNG Hunters have lost their Round 10 clash to Townsville Blackhawks 36 - 26 this evening at the Jack Manski Oval, Townsville, Australia.
The Hunters started the match slowly, trailing 10 - 24 in the first half, with the host putting on a dominant display. 
Paul Aiton's men started the second half on strong terms with two consecutive tries, but the home side showed resilience to seal the win with two late tries. 
The try scorers for PNG Hunters include Brendon Nima, Alex Max, Finley Glare, and Gairo Voro, with a double. 
The Hunters host Northern Pride next Sunday in Port Moresby.

snippet.title: SpaceX Starship Flight 9
snippet.description:
The first launch attempt for Starship Flight 9 with Booster 14-2 and Ship 35 from Pad A, Starbase, Earth. The window for the launch opens at 18:30 local time (23:30 UTC) on Tuesday, May 27. 

This mission will not include a catch of Booster 14, as the Booster will splashdown in the Gulf. Ship 35 will be the focus of this test flight, as SpaceX aims to perform a successful SECO with the upgraded Block 2 version, follow two consecutive flights which failed to reach that milestone.

Ship 35 is the third Block 2 Ship, featuring several upgrades to mitigate the problems suffered during Flights 7 and 8.

snippet.title: What if you used a flamethrower as a snowblower?
snippet.description:
Get a copy of What If? 2 and Randall’s other books at: https://xkcd.com/books
More serious answers to absurd questions at: https://what-if.xkcd.com/

This question comes from Matt, who asks: I've long thought about putting a flamethrower on the front of a car to melt snow and ice before you drive across it. Now I've realized that a flamethrower is impractical, but what about a high-powered microwave emitter?


Credits
*******
Randall Munroe | Narrator
Henry Reich | Writer & Director 
Lizah van der Aart | Illustration and Video Editing
Ever Salazar | Chief Chaos Controller
Know Art Studios | Music & Sound Effects

What If? The Video Series is the official adaptation of the What If? books by Randall Munroe and is produced by Neptune Studios LLC.

snippet.title: My Honda-Swapped FWD '65 Mustang LIVES AGAIN! (then breaks)
snippet.description:
UNSEEN CARS AND VIDEOS: https://patreon.com/tomsrefurbraw  

NEW MERCH: https://tomsrefurb.shop

SPEEDY'S EQUIPMENT: https://speedysequipment.com

It's finally time to bring back MASUTANGU! This is my homebuilt 1965 Mustang that started as a no-title coupe shell that we body-swapped it onto a turbocharged, B20-powered Honda Civic chassis. Love you all!

snippet.title: Guilty Gear -Strive- Starter Guide - Unika
snippet.description:
■Official website: https://www.guiltygear.com/ggst/jp/
GUILTY GEAR : the next entry to the series
「GUILTY GEAR」シリーズ最新作「GUILTY GEAR -STRIVE-」

【ゲーム内容】
常に"最先端"を生み出し続ける「ギルティギア」シリーズが贈る最新作『GUILTY GEAR -STRIVE-』 洗練されたシステム、極まるアニメーション映像、個性あふれるキャラクターによる、手に汗握るぶつかり合いの連続を体感せよ！

◆超美麗、手描きアニメと見紛うグラフィック！
手描きアニメにしか見えない超美麗グラフィックは更に進化。細部まで徹底的にこだわり抜いた新世代の映像表現！

◆格闘ゲームの最先端！
対戦格闘の新機軸を目指して制作された本作。プレイヤーの裾野を広げつつ、ギルティギアらしい奥深いゲーム性を両立。ステージ端を取り払う大胆なギミックをはじめ、格闘ゲームならではの熱い読み合いを生み出す緻密なシステム。

◆因縁、決着！
25年に渡り紡がれてきたギルティギアの奥深いストーリー。描かれてきた数々の因縁がついに決着！そして明かされる驚愕の真実とは――

【ストーリー】
脅威の元凶「慈悲無き啓示」を討ち倒したソル＝バッドガイ。
再び手に入れた休息を楽しむ暇もなく、彼の元に驚愕のニュースが飛び込んで来た。

GEARを生み出し聖戦を引き起こし、人類史上最大最悪の大罪人と呼ばれる「あの男」こと「飛鳥＝R＝クロイツ」が米国政府に投降したのだ。

自分をGEARに改造した男。積年の復讐の相手であり、かつての親友でもある。
真意を推し量りながら、ソルは得物を手に立ち上がるのだった。

―――「あの男」との因縁に決着（ケリ）をつけるために。

© ARC SYSTEM WORKS

#GGST #GUILTYGEAR #ギルティギア #ギルティギアストライヴ #ユニカ  #GGSTDR

snippet.title: We Built a Tiny Log Cabin
snippet.description:
Our latest dream project: building a teeny, tiny log cabin in the woods! Who do you think will get the most use out of it? Start your free trial today by going to https://www.shopify.com/eamonandbec 
What would you add to Frankie's tiny cabin?? Let us know in the comments below :):)

0:00 let's build a tiny cabin!!
1:45 here's the building plans
5:04 gathering logs from our property
11:20 the playhouse structure begins
16:54 OMG! this is so cool!
18:36 BTS of our company
21:11 putting on the roof
24:00 Frankie's reaction
26:15 grand reveal 

We moved out to our cabin in the woods 5 years ago & since then we've entered a new season of life with babies all around us (nieces, nephews, friends with children and a toddler of our own!). Even though there is never ending nature up here and a plethora of fun activities the kids always can't wait to go home to head to their local park soooooooo...
Today, we're taking on one of our dream projects --- building a tiny log cabin playhouse for our 1.5 year old daughter Frankie, right here at our off-grid cabin in the woods! From the first cut to the final nail, we're creating a magical little space where she can play, explore and grow. 

Join us as we share the process of DIY log cabin building, the challenges of working off-grid and the pure joy of seeing Frankie's reaction for the first time. Whether you're a fan of tiny homes, homesteading life, or family vlogs, this video is packed with inspiration for creating meaningful spaces with your loved ones. 

We're Eamon & Bec ((and Oso) and now Frankie!!). We once lived very minimally out of vans #vanlife but happily moved into the woods during the pandemic #cabinlife . When we found out we were going to have a baby we decided to also rent an apartment in the city so we can be surrounded by the support of both our families which means that we only spend a few good months of the year at our cabin. We're super excited for the many summer projects we have on the horizon!

इस बिल्ड में सब कुछ था- चुपके मिशन, भेस, 11-फुट की ट्रॉफी और एक छिपा हुआ कमरा जो अंतरिक्ष यान की तरह जगमगाता था। सबसे पागलपन भरा हिस्सा? मिस्टरबीस्ट, मार्क रॉबर्ट, फ़ेज़ रग और दुनिया के कई सबसे बड़े यूट्यूबर्स बस कुछ ही फीट की दूरी पर थे और उन्हें बिल्कुल भी अंदाज़ा नहीं था कि असल में क्या हो रहा है।

अगर आप यह पढ़ रहे हैं तो आप असली हैं!

टिप्पणी करें “मुझे एक गुप्त कमरा चाहिए!” ताकि मैं आपको नोटिस कर सकूँ।

संयुक्त राज्य अमेरिका बनाम स्पेनिश निर्माता!, लेकिन HABLA HISPANA बनाम ESTADOS UNIDOS 🏀, लेकिन मैंने अपनी बहन से छुपने के लिए एक गुप्त गेमिंग रूम बनाया, लेकिन मैंने अपनी माँ से छुपने के लिए एक गुप्त गेमिंग रूम बनाया, लेकिन मैं प्रसिद्ध YouTuber के वीडियो में छिपा ... किसी ने ध्यान नहीं दिया, लेकिन मैंने मिस्टरबीस्ट के लिए एक गुप्त कमरा बनाया, लेकिन मैंने अपने कमरे में एक गुप्त पूल बनाया, लेकिन मैंने एकांत कारावास में 7 दिन बिताए नायेरसिना, इबाई, चैंडलर हॉलो, मार्क रॉबर्ट, फेडे विगेवानी, स्टोक्स ट्विन्स, मिस्टरबीस्ट, रिकी लिमोन, डी'वॉन्टे फ्रिगा, जुएगाजर्मन, फेज़ रग या एयररैक बनाएंगे। यह एक ऐसा वीडियो है जिसमें मैथ्यू बीम (उर्फ एमबीम10) ने फेडे के यूट्यूबर बास्केटबॉल टूर्नामेंट के दौरान एयररैक को छिपाने के लिए मिस्टरबीस्ट के गोदाम के अंदर एक गुप्त गेमिंग रूम बनाया था!

MrBeast, Mark Rober, FaZe Rug y un montón de los YouTubers más famosos del planeta estaban a solo unos metros de distancia sin tener ni idea de lo que estaba pasando.

Si estás leyendo esto, ¡eres uno de verdad!

pa.title: ਮੈਂ 5,000,000 ਡਾਲਰ ਖਰਚ ਕੀਤੇ ਤਾਂ ਜੋ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਫ੍ਰੀ ਵਿੱਚ ਸਪੇਸ ਵਿੱਚ ਜਾ ਸਕੋ।
pa.description:
ਆਪਣੀ ਬਿਲਕੁਲ ਫ੍ਰੀ ਸੈਲਫੀ ਲਓ ਅਤੇ ਫਿਰ ਆਪਣੀ ਸਭ ਤੋਂ ਘੱਟ ਬੋਰਿੰਗ ਗਰਮੀਆਂ ਲਈ ਸਪੇਸ ਕੈਂਪ ਕ੍ਰੰਚਲੈਬਸ 'ਤੇ ਮੇਰੇ ਨਾਲ ਸ਼ਾਮਲ ਹੋਵੋ: https://crunchlabs.com/SpaceCamp
ਆਪਣੀ ਖੁਦ ਦੀ ਸਪੇਸ ਸੈਲਫੀ ਫ੍ਰੀ ਵਿੱਚ ਇੱਥੇ ਪ੍ਰਾਪਤ ਕਰੋ: http://spaceselfie.com
ਟੀ-ਮੋਬਾਈਲ 'ਤੇ ਮੇਰੇ ਦੋਸਤਾਂ ਦਾ ਬਹੁਤ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ, ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਦੀ ਸਫਲਤਾਪੂਰਵਕ ਸੈਟੇਲਾਈਟ ਕਵਰੇਜ ਵੱਲ ਤਰੱਕੀ ਦੇ ਜਸ਼ਨ ਵਿੱਚ ਇਸ ਪ੍ਰੋਜੈਕਟ ਦਾ ਸਮਰਥਨ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ।
ਤੁਹਾਡੀ ਸੈਲਫੀ। ਗੂਗਲ ਪਿਕਸਲ 'ਤੇ ਪ੍ਰਦਰਸ਼ਿਤ। ਸਪੇਸ ਵਿੱਚ। ਹੋਰ ਅੱਪਡੇਟਾਂ ਲਈ @teampixel ਨੂੰ ਫਾਲੋ ਕਰੋ! https://www.instagram.com/teampixel/ #googlepartner
ਇਸ ਸ਼ਾਨਦਾਰ ਬਿਲਡ ਵਿੱਚ ਮਦਦ ਕਰਨ ਵਾਲੇ ਹਰ ਵਿਅਕਤੀ ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ:
ਟਾਇਵਾਕ ਇੰਟਰਨੈਸ਼ਨਲ 'ਤੇ ਸਾਡੀ ਬਿਲਡ ਟੀਮ ਦਾ SATGUS ਨੂੰ ਜੀਵਨ ਵਿੱਚ ਲਿਆਉਣ ਵਿੱਚ ਸਾਡੀ ਮਦਦ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ! https://tyvak.eu/
ਕੋਲੋਰਾਡੋ ਸਕੂਲ ਆਫ਼ ਮਾਈਨਜ਼ ਵਿਖੇ ਐਕਸਪਲੋਸਿਵਜ਼ ਰਿਸਰਚ ਲੈਬ ਦਾ ਵਿਸ਼ੇਸ਼ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ https://erl.mines.edu/
ਵੀਡੀਓ ਵਿੱਚ ਕੁਝ ਮਿਊਜ਼ਿਕ ਦੇਣ ਲਈ ਇਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਲੋਕਾਂ ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ:

snippet.title: Superwood is Here! This Amazing New Material Could Change The World!
snippet.description:
Thanks to Tecovas for sponsoring this video! Visit https://tecovas.yt.link/A6Z5KBV to get your new favorite pair of boots today!

Superwood is a revolutionary material engineered to reshape the future of construction.  It is stronger than steel, lighter than steel and costs less than steel - and now it is so much more than just a theory.  A new company, InventWood has been set up and has over $50 million dollars in funding to turn their research into practical products.

Superwood is Densified wood that is created through a couple of simple processes that increase it's strength while keeping the natural warmth of real wood.  In this video, we’ll break down how Superwood is made and how it can be stronger than steel.  We'll also discuss the game changing impact that it could have on the world, as well as some potential problems.

Could Superwood really replace steel and other traditional building materials? Leave me a comment and let me know your thoughts.

snippet.title: Daily Round Up - Day 01 | 2025 Isle of Man TT Races
snippet.description:
Day 1 at the Isle of Man TT Races and the Newcomers get their first taste of the mountain course under their belt, just before the weather delays action for the day. Chris Pritchard and Mike Booth catch up with John McGuinness MBE and Dean Harrison in the paddock, in their Honda Factory awning.

John reflects on his first time on the course as a newcomer, and they discuss riding in wet conditions, tyres and testing. Find out what their expectations are for TT 2025.
_______________________________________________

snippet.title: Do Thin Oils Destroy Engines? Lessons From GM’s Massive Recall
snippet.description:
After 28,000 engine failures, GM is recommending thicker oil. Will it work?
Do Thin Oils Damage Engines - https://youtu.be/IKdhgKUZhPA
Subscribe to Engineering Explained for more videos! - https://goo.gl/VZstk7

After over 28,000 reported engine failures, GM is recommending thicker oil as a potential solution — but is that really the answer? In this video, we take a deep dive into why so many GM 6.2L V8 (L87) engines are failing, what the actual root causes are, and why a simple oil change is being offered as a fix in some cases.

We’ll explore:
1. The manufacturing flaws behind these widespread failures.
2. How oil viscosity and the Stribeck Curve relate to engine wear.
3. Whether thinner oils are causing damage in modern engines.
4. If switching to a thicker oil could actually help protect your engine.

This isn’t just opinion — we’re digging into the data, published research, and real-world test results to understand the logic behind GM’s service bulletins and what it means for both affected vehicles and the broader debate around oil viscosity. If you’re curious about the science behind engine lubrication, the role of modern manufacturing, or just want to understand what oil you should be using, this video is for you.

GM Engine Recall Motor Oil Geek - https://youtu.be/pbEdr6Q6cKw

snippet.title: Carín León, Maluma - Si Tú Me Vieras [Official Video]
snippet.description:
🦁 Suscríbete a mi canal: 

Mi nuevo álbum “Palabra de To’s (Seca)" ya está disponible en todas las plataformas: 
https://carinleon.lnk.to/PalabraDeTosSeca

LETRA👇:

Tengo un millón de personas y me siento solitario,
porque no siento tu aroma,
porque no siento tus labios.

De tanto estar desvelado, 
ya se me cambió el horario,
y yo no sé si tú recuerdas,
ayer fue el aniversario.
Todavía me lo recuerda el calendario,
aunque hace daño.

Si tú me vieras cómo tomo,para ver si borracho te olvido.
Si tú me vieras cómo sufro,asimilando que no estás conmigo.
Si tú me vieras, malgastándome las horas viendo nuestras fotos.
Si tú me vieras, cómo hablo con el silencio cosas de nosotros.
Si tú me vieras,si tú me vieras...
Seguramente otra oportunidad me dieras.

Reina,vuelva.
Hagamos que lo nuestro se resuelva.
Si algo de mí en tu vida se conserva, 
entoncesvamos a intentarlo de nuevo.
Tomando a tu nombre, una semana llevo.
Yo sé que superarte debo,
pero tu nombre vuelve cuando bebo.

Aunque no parezca,
estoy hablando con el corazón, 
para que te compadezcas.
Ya tomaste tu decisión, pero...

snippet.title: I was not expecting the POLICE to show up MID-JOB
snippet.description:
Use code FATHERS2025 to get 20% off ALL MERCH at https://sbmowing.com/shop

I found this house on the corner of the Main Street and the sidewalks, curbs, and grass were getting crazy overgrown. So, I knocked on the door and didn’t get an answer and the neighbor told me he hasn’t seen anyone here for 3 to 4 weeks. So I decided I would go ahead and get it cleaned up for the neighborhood. During the edging along the main road, I was playing leap frog as the cars came by. About halfway down the curb, a cop pulled up and I thought I might be in trouble. They didn’t get out, so I finished real quick and went to talk to them. Turns out, they were doing me a HUGE favor, so be sure to stay to see the full interaction I had with them.
